#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:25
msgid "Using the Project Bin"
msgstr "De project-bin gebruiken"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:27
msgid ""
"The Project Bin\\ [1]_ is where all your :term:`assets<Asset>` are. "
"Depending on the size of your project, that list can quickly become "
"confusing and difficult to work with. Kdenlive has several features to "
"manage the bin's content."
msgstr ""
"De project-bin\\ [1]_ is waar al uw :term:`bezittingen<Asset>` zich "
"bevinden. Afhankelijk van de grootte van uw project kan die lijst snel "
"verwarrend en moeilijk mee te werken zijn. Kdenlive heeft verschillende "
"mogelijkheden on de inhoud van bin te beheren."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:31
msgid "User Interface"
msgstr "Gebruikersinterface"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:39
msgid "The Project Bin in Kdenlive"
msgstr "De project-bin in Kdenlive"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:46
msgid "**1**"
msgstr "**1**"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:47
msgid ""
"|kdenlive-add-clip|\\ :guilabel:`Add clip or folder` opens a window similar "
"to the file manager of your OS allowing you to navigate around your file "
"system and select :doc:`files to be added</project_and_asset_management/"
"project_bin/clips>` to the project bin."
msgstr ""
"|kdenlive-add-clip|\\ :guilabel:`Clip of map openen` opent een venster "
"gelijk aan de bestandsbeheerder van uw OS waarmee u kunt navigeren in uw "
"bestandssysteem en :doc:`toe te voegen bestanden</"
"project_and_asset_management/project_bin/clips>` aan de project-bin "
"selecteert."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:49
msgid ""
"|go-down| opens a pop-up window from where you can select what kind of clip "
"you want to add"
msgstr ""
"|go-down| opent een pop-up-venster waaruit u kunt selecteren welk soort clip "
"u wilt toevoegen"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:51
msgid ""
"|folder-new|\\ :guilabel:`Add folder` creates a :doc:`new folder</"
"project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use_folders>` in the "
"current project bin. These are virtual folders that help you organize large "
"bins. Folders can be turned into their own bins."
msgstr ""
"|folder-new|\\ :guilabel:`Map toevoegen` maakt een :doc:`nieuwe map</"
"project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use_folders>` in de "
"huidige project-bin. Dit zijn virtuele mappen die u helpen om grote bins te "
"beheren. Mappen kunnen omgedraaid worden in hun eigen bins."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:52
msgid "**2**"
msgstr "**2**"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:53
msgid ""
"|edit-delete|\\ :guilabel:`Delete clip or folder` deletes the currently "
"selected clip or folder from the bin"
msgstr ""
"|edit-delete|\\ :guilabel:`Clip of map verwijderen` verwijdert de nu "
"geselecteerde clip of map uit de bin"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:54
msgid "**3**"
msgstr "**3**"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:55
msgid ""
"|tag|\\ :guilabel:`Tags Panel` toggles the :ref:"
"`tags<project_bin_using_tags>` panel"
msgstr ""
"|tag|\\ :guilabel:`Tags Paneel` schakelt het :ref:"
"`tags<project_bin_using_tags>` paneel in en uit"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:56
msgid "**4**"
msgstr "**4**"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:57
msgid ""
"|application-menu|\\ :guilabel:`Options` opens a pop-window with more "
"`options` including the option to :ref:`scale <scaling_the_view>` the view"
msgstr ""
"|application-menu|\\ :guilabel:`Opties` opent een popup-venster met meer "
"`opties` inclusief de mogelijkheid om de weergave te :ref:`verschalen <"
"scaling_the_view>`"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:58
msgid "**5**"
msgstr "**5**"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:59
msgid ""
"|view-filter|\\ :guilabel:`Filter` switches a :ref:"
"`filter<project_bin_using_filters>` on or off"
msgstr ""
"|view-filter|\\ :guilabel:`Filter` schakelt een :ref:"
"`filter<project_bin_using_filters>` aan of uit"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:61
msgid ""
"|go-down|\\ :guilabel:`Filter` opens a pop-up window to :doc:`set "
"filter<project_bin_use_filters>` parameters"
msgstr ""
"|go-down|\\ :guilabel:`Filter` opent een pop-up venster om de :doc:`filter"
" instellingen<project_bin_use_filters>` te wijzigen"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:62
msgid "**6**"
msgstr "**6**"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:63
msgid ""
"Search field to :ref:`search for "
"assets<project_bin_searching_the_project_bin>` in the bin"
msgstr ""
"Invoerveld voor :ref:`zoeken naar objecten<project_bin_searching_the_project_b"
"in>` in de bin"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:64
msgid "**7**"
msgstr "**7**"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:65
msgid ""
"|go-up|\\ :guilabel:`Sort` Toggles between sorting ascending and descending"
msgstr "|go-up|\\ :guilabel:`Sorteren` Schakelt om tussen oplopend en aflopend"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:66
msgid "**8**"
msgstr "**8**"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:67
msgid ""
"The folder with all the sequences. It is there even if you did not :doc:"
"`create a sequence</project_and_asset_management/project_bin/sequence>`."
msgstr ""
"De map met alle sequenties. Het is daar zelfs als u nog geen :doc:"
"`sequentie heeft gecreëerd</project_and_asset_management/project_bin/sequence"
">`."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:68
msgid "**9**"
msgstr "**9**"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:69
msgid ""
"Folders created by the user (for illustration purposes only). You can turn "
"folders into :ref:`individual bins<project_bin_using_multiple_bins>` that "
"can be added to your workspace and docked."
msgstr ""
"Mappen gecreëerd door de gebruiker (hier alleen als illustratie). Mappen"
" kunnen worden omgezet naar :ref:`individuele bins<"
